lines: 1. Mogambi one, ninkobake,'Bonene nobwao,Tinyeb'egutwa y'amagwa,Ndae goika Kalwari.
Tinyeba Gethesemane,Tinyeb'emechando yao;Tinyeb'obwanchani bwao,Ndae goika Kalwari.
3. Nainche bun'ere Mariamu,Nchiche n'ekeegwa;Nyorokie oboina bwasie,Ndae goika kalwari.
4. Omonene nimbogorie,'Mosalaba rioka;Nsange emechando yaye,Kwambogoreirie onsi.
